n好可能黑警會自行私了<br />\n到時就慘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a5b40b700b0a2f16a158d551cab78e911f485b","tid":1957574,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a45c32602cb71939ee484a3383d9c9e8c97f10","tid":1957574,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"連企圖謀殺，縱火呢啲可以終身嘅都唔上高院<br />\n估都估到咩事<br />\n港共覺得7年都夠<br />\n好過冒險上高院結果甩咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"企圖謀殺有唔上高院咩？<br />\n定係你誤會左過堂係審訊咋"},{"pid":"f4423239e6bdeb1e427890baa86e8c26036af71c","tid":1957574,"uid":230662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:57:19.000Z","msg":"只可以話，唔樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔覺得每一個黃都咁堅定覺得抗爭有理，義士無恥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edd57047a36000a4778aabe96da0a2763052b7e","tid":1957574,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99edd484a6a0a1ff38ec2e12adc6a937fd42440","tid":1957574,"uid":181474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"50793ceffb5921cb38d2039195ec1b6f7b735ba5","tid":1957574,"uid":144262,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"0bbb129bc7c3cbf44de1d6c7f29f511c857d0656","tid":1957574,"uid":281054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:00:10.000Z","msg":"no <br />\n舉個例<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">打你一下</span> 坐十年<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">殺咗你</span> 冇事<br />\n至於點解 請睇上面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"地區法院最多判7年<br />\n所以黑警會盡量將啲控罪改到最多7年再擺落地方法院<br />\n至於大單嘢要上高院嗰啲<br />\n好可能黑警會自行私了<br />\n到時就慘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"唔係改，根本大部分可公訴罪行（即係比較嚴重既罪行），控方係可以根據案情嚴重性決定係咩法院審。<br />\n<br />\n如控罪之相關法例條文包含「一經 公訴程序」或「循公訴程序」的字眼，該罪行便是可公訴罪行。多數可公訴罪行可於裁判法院、區域法院或高等法院原訟法庭審理。<span style=\"color: red;\">控方有權選擇由哪一個法庭審理可公訴罪行（《刑事訴訟程序條例》（第221章）第14條），主要取決於案件的複雜性及可能判處之刑罰。舉例，如案件的判刑可能是監禁 4 年，控方便會選擇於區域法院進行審訊（因區域法院最多可判監 7 年），而不會選擇由裁判法院進行審訊（因裁判法院之最高監禁刑期只是 2 年）。</span><br />\n<br />\n有些較嚴重的可公訴罪行不能在裁判法院審理，它們列於《裁判官條例》（第227章）附表2之第 I 部，其中包括販毒及鎗擊案。列於上述附表第 III 部之罪行（例如謀殺或誤殺）只能於高等法院原訟法庭由法官會同陪審團審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/court_procedure/q2.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FpoliceAndCrime%2Fcourt_procedure%2Fq2.shtml&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQypnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=0e1991b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/policeAndCrime/court_procedure/q2.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"43eaf610c14a41b57badb57148c14974dba08aa7","tid":1957574,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83f0be1b0bceefc84890ddfe415ec2438b89a315","tid":1957574,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24b00d1136e08a8659357d139642a69e6e03bf91","tid":1957574,"uid":144262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:14:32.000Z","msg":"依家冇一單case上到高院<br />\n因為港共唔想你知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原來係可以咁做！</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T23:02:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你啱<br />\n終於有人睇得穿發生咩事<br />\n我本來都係依排中選嘅陪審團<br />\n最後法院借助武肺一事搞到近排嘅陪審團全部「豁免」無得做<br />\n仲要免除2年內再抽中<br />\n完全幫唔到任何手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">法治已死</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"咁都叫法治已死我諗全世界每個國家法治一日都死幾百次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf4bef46e8ff272544ebe3a43c139769bb530fc","tid":1957574,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50793ceffb5921cb38d2039195ec1b6f7b735ba5","tid":1957574,"